            <MainPageContent>
                <p id='FAQTop' class="faq-content-entry">
                    See our <a href='/Intro/Overview'>overview page</a> for information about the <em>OET</em> translation philosophy and the various <em>OET</em> versions.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Note: Some of the design of the <em>OET</em> is still in flux, so please regard the answers to these FAQs as current snapshots only.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Use the <a href='/About/Contact'>contact page</a> to submit additional questions.
                </p>
                <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p class="faq-content-entry"><a href='#Download'>Where can I download the <em>OET</em> from?</a></p>
                <p class="faq-content-entry"><a href='#SoLong'>Why's the <em>OET</em> taking so long?</a></p>
                <p class="faq-content-entry"><a href='#SoMany'>Why are there so many translations?</a></p>
                <p class="faq-content-entry"><a href='#Different'>Why is the <em>OET</em> different from other translations?</a></p>
